79
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:40,560
Personal honor is collective honor.

80
00:03:40,720 --> 00:03:41,190
Right?

81
00:03:41,290 --> 00:03:43,120
Don't you feel guilty about the station

82
00:03:43,170 --> 00:03:44,580
and every fireman here?

83
00:03:44,580 --> 00:03:45,900
You're not worried,

84
