it's for honor.

93
00:03:58,650 --> 00:03:59,160
Right?

94
00:03:59,480 --> 00:04:00,810
Maybe there will be bonuses and subsidies.

95
00:04:01,230 --> 00:04:02,270
Who told you that?

96
00:04:02,420 --> 00:04:03,020
I mean maybe.

97
00:04:03,190 --> 00:04:04,540
We can't miss out on that chance.

98
00:04:05,320 --> 00:04:06,120
Maybe?

99
