146
00:05:29,320 --> 00:05:31,320
We worked all day

147
00:05:31,320 --> 00:05:33,400
and were hungry after coming back so we ordered takeout. What the hell…

148
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:38,280
To be honest,

149
00:05:38,320 --> 00:05:39,120
Instructor,

150
00:05:39,510 --> 00:05:40,920
you found serious negligence

151
00:05:40,920 --> 00:05:42,720
and misconduct in our work.

152
00:05:43,160 --> 00:05:46,080
It must be seriously addressed.

153
00:05:46,550 --> 00:05:47,880
Tell everyone not on duty

154
00:05:47,960 --> 00:05:49,800
to come for a meeting in the activity room three minutes later.

155
00:05:53,520 --> 00:05:54,320
Meeting?

156
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:55,730
Lately,

157
00:05:56,390 --> 00:05:58,480
a video about us

158
00:05:58,600 --> 00:06:00,880
has been widely spread online

159
00:06:01,210 --> 00:06:02,780
and caused a lot of controversy.

160
00:06:02,900 --> 00:06:05,280
We've left the public

161
00:06:05,330 --> 00:06:06,900
with a bad impression.

162
00:06:07,690 --> 00:06:08,710
I hope every one of us

163
00:06:09,080 --> 00:06:11,350
can spend some time reflecting on it.

164
00:06:12,350 --> 00:06:14,200
It can't happen again.

165
00:06:15,070 --> 00:06:15,860
So,

166
00:06:16,350 --> 00:06:17,030
I suggest

167
00:06:17,590 --> 00:06:20,860
building a supply depot in our station.

168
00:06:22,060 --> 00:06:23,860
When we come back from a mission

169
00:06:24,150 --> 00:06:25,260
and feel hungry,

170
00:06:25,550 --> 00:06:26,670
we can go there to eat.

171
00:06:27,070 --> 00:06:28,420
There are no limits

172
00:06:28,420 --> 00:06:29,110
on the food types.

173
00:06:29,500 --> 00:06:31,030
You can have

174
00:06:31,300 --> 00:06:32,820
bread and cookies,

175
00:06:32,940 --> 00:06:34,540
chips and sausages,

176
00:06:34,620 --> 00:06:36,270
or instant noodles.

177
00:06:36,380 --> 00:06:37,180
If you want,

178
00:06:37,380 --> 00:06:39,780
you can also roast chicken and cook steaks.

179
00:06:40,100 --> 00:06:41,660
I'll prepare a fridge for you.

180
00:06:42,100 --> 00:06:45,340
Of course, the instructor agrees with it.

181
00:06:45,540 --> 00:06:48,620
He's very concerned about our health.

182
00:06:48,620 --> 00:06:50,420
Let's give him a big hand.

183
00:06:50,550 --> 00:06:52,030
Great!

184
00:06:53,270 --> 00:06:54,060
