186
00:07:01,270 --> 00:07:02,380
Any comment?

187
00:07:02,540 --> 00:07:02,950
Liu Ruyi.

188
00:07:03,300 --> 00:07:03,620
Yes.

189
00:07:04,060 --> 00:07:05,260
