190
00:07:05,670 --> 00:07:06,220
Yes.

191
00:07:06,980 --> 00:07:08,500
Director Lin hit the nail on the head.

192
00:07:08,580 --> 00:07:11,100
Instructor Yang saw the core of the problem.

193
00:07:11,260 --> 00:07:11,980
Thank you, Director Lin!

194
00:07:12,020 --> 00:07:12,980
Thank you, Instructor Yang!

195
00:07:13,060 --> 00:07:14,660
Thank you for caring so much for us.

196
00:07:14,660 --> 00:07:15,220
