this supply depot ourselves?

241
00:08:30,150 --> 00:08:31,340
Shut up.

242
00:08:31,420 --> 00:08:31,900
Seriously?

243
00:08:32,180 --> 00:08:33,620
You never miss the point.

244
00:08:34,180 --> 00:08:34,980
Well,

245
00:08:35,390 --> 00:08:36,900
let me make it clear.

246
00:08:37,060 --> 00:08:38,420
You don't have to

247
00:08:38,580 --> 00:08:40,820
pay for this supply depot.

248
00:08:40,820 --> 00:08:42,750
