257
00:09:10,380 --> 00:09:11,310
See? They're so happy.

258
00:09:11,750 --> 00:09:12,350
Classic you.

259
00:09:12,820 --> 00:09:14,180
You love stirring the pot.

260
00:09:15,580 --> 00:09:16,500
Enough.

261
00:09:16,740 --> 00:09:17,500
Be quiet.

262
00:09:18,180 --> 00:09:19,100
I got it.

263
00:09:20,180 --> 00:09:21,390
