267
00:09:26,500 --> 00:09:27,580
Since you want to eat,

268
00:09:27,780 --> 00:09:29,620
you should eat well.

269
00:09:29,700 --> 00:09:30,540
If necessary,

270
00:09:30,540 --> 00:09:31,940
you can cook here.

271
00:09:32,140 --> 00:09:32,750
Understand?

272
00:09:32,860 --> 00:09:34,500
Don't do anything stupid again.

273
00:09:34,540 --> 00:09:36,420
Especially some of you.

274
00:09:36,860 --> 00:09:38,460
You know who I mean,

275
00:09:38,900 --> 00:09:39,270
don't you?

276
00:09:39,980 --> 00:09:43,030
Don't eat too many

277
00:09:43,900 --> 00:09:44,380
snacks and desserts.

278
00:09:44,380 --> 00:09:45,020
Okay.

279
00:09:45,060 --> 00:09:45,820
Right?

280
00:09:46,260 --> 00:09:47,900
